ews/music/listen-to-tyler-the-creators-huge-new-album-chromakopia-now-3806980">Chromakopia</a> 》中他们共同创作的《Balloon》的表演。</p><p>观看以下两场表演的粉丝捕捉视频： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Doechii 和 SZA 在 2024 年 Camp Flog Gnaw 上表演“Persuasive”" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VcobZAV5ODE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@withoutwarningnewyork/video/7438039793897983262" data-video-id="7438039793897983262" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width:605px; min-width:325px;"><section> <a target="_blank" title="@没有警告纽约" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@withoutwarningnewyork?refer=embed">@没有警告纽约</a></p><p>疯狂联署<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f525.png" alt="🔥" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f525.png" alt="🔥" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a title="多吉伊" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/doechii?refer=embed">#doechii</a> <a title="萨" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/sza?refer=embed">#sza</a> <a title="营弗洛格瑙" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/campfloggnaw?refer=embed">#campfloggnaw</a> <a title="营弗洛格纳2024" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/campfloggnaw2024?refer=embed">#campfloggnaw202​​4</a></p><p> <a target="_blank" title="♬ 原声 - 没有警告" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7438039742698048287?refer=embed">♬ 原声 – 没有警告</a></section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Tyler, The Creator 与 Doechii 在 2024 年 Camp Flog Gnaw 上表演“气球”" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wAg_QwQuMCA?feature=oembed&enablejsap